{"title":"桥","authors":["于书恒"],"dates":[{"year":1998,"month":9,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"桥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于书恒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学校前面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"横着一条拦路的小河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新架起的小桥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把腰弓着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让孩子们在它背上通过。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小桥说，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是模仿一位老师的动作，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当年他也是弓着腰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"背起这座山村小学。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}